WEBVTT

00:02:59.004 --> 00:03:01.391
watoto wanatakiwa watoke
katika hitari nne:

00:03:01.415 --> 00:03:03.988
aa, aB, aa, Ba.

00:03:04.884 --> 00:03:07.173
Badala yake katika ubadilishaji jeni,

00:03:07.197 --> 00:03:08.709
wote walitokea aB.

00:03:09.900 --> 00:03:12.452
Kibiolojia, hiyo haitakiwi
hata kuwezekana.

00:03:12.476 --> 00:03:13.780
Sasa nini kilichotokea?

00:03:14.709 --> 00:03:16.153
Kitu cha kwanza kilichotokea

00:03:16.177 --> 00:03:19.447
ni kuwasili kifaa cha kuhakiki jeni
kilichoitwa CRISPR mwaka 2012.

00:03:20.701 --> 00:03:22.811
wengi wenu pengine
mmesikia kuhusu CRISPR,

00:03:22.835 --> 00:03:26.136
hivyo kwa kifupi hiyo CRISPR
ni kifaa kinachoruhusu watafiti

00:03:26.160 --> 00:03:28.739
kuhakiki jeni kwa uhakika,
kirahisi na haraka.

00:03:29.533 --> 00:03:33.262
Inafanya hivi kwa kuunganisha utaratibu
ambao ulikuwepo ndani ya bakteria.